title.Name: title
title.Value: Martial Arts, Aikido, Manila Aikido Club (Demo 02) by Dundee Santos, Philippines

description.Name: description
description.Value: Soft Style Aikido, Aikido Hard Style (1), MAC Senior Senseis (3), Traditional Aikido (4), Modern Aikido / Practical Aikido (5), MAC 49th Anniv.(6), MAC Aikido Lessons (7), Aikido Ukemi (8), Disarming Techniques (9), Aikido Randori (10). Soft Style and some traditional aikido were demonstrated in this video. The techniques performed here in not applicable in real self defense. But this practice will develop the form, balance and precise application of the technique. Also, it enhances the blending of Nage & Uke.
